casebody.data:
No. 10-6618. John-Pierre Baney, Petitioner v. Merit Systems Protection Board. 562 U.S. 1194, 131 S. Ct. 999,

178 L. Ed. 2d 855,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 704, January 18, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Leave to proceed as a veteran granted. *856Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.

Same case below, 360 Fed. Appx. 119.
